sets.subTitle: Centr Power in Gym: Advanced week 1

workouts.title: Workout
workouts.introText:
This session is all about bringing the burn to your shoulders to grow, shape and strengthen.


Good form is essential to protect (and grow) your shoulders, so head to the exercise tutorial before you hit the racks.

groups.title: Warm-up
groups.summary: Fire up your muscles and get your joints moving smoothly.

groups.title: Round 1
groups.summary: Engage your core – you're going to need it here!

groups.title: Round 2
groups.summary: Press like an action hero for this killer deltoid shaper.

groups.title: Round 3
groups.summary: Good form is crucial on these raises, so look to Bobby if you need a refresher.

groups.title: Round 4
groups.summary: You'll feel this in the rear of your shoulders tomorrow.

groups.title: Round 5
groups.summary: Work your traps and rhomboids for broad and strong shoulders.

groups.title: Round 6
groups.summary: While your core is crunching, your shoulders will be working to stabilize the plate. Make it steady and strong.
